SIMPLE: marvel
RECORDS: 3

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Marvel
<hw>Mar"vel</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>mervaile</ets>, F. <ets>merveille</ets>, fr. L.
<ets>mirabilia</ets> wonderful things, pl., fr. <ets>mirabilis</ets>
wonderful, fr. <ets>mirari</ets> to wonder or marvel at. See
<er>Admire</er>, <er>Smile</er>, and cf. <er>Miracle</er>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>That which causes wonder; a prodigy; a
miracle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I will do <qex>marvels</qex> such as have not been done.</q>
<rj><qau>Ex. xxxiv. 10.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Nature's sweet <qex>marvel</qex> undefiled.</q>
<rj><qau>Emerson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Wonder.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Use lessens
<xex>marvel</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Sir W. Scott.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>marvel-of-Peru</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>marvel of Peru</ent>⟦br⟧
<mhw>

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Marvel
<hw>Mar"vel</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos>
<conjf>Marveled</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr> or <conjf>Marvelled</conjf>;
<pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos> <conjf>Marveling</conjf> or
<conjf>Marvelling</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[OE. <ets>merveilen</ets>, OF.
<ets>merveillier</ets>.]</ety> <def>To be struck with surprise,
astonishment, or wonder; to wonder.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Marvel</qex> not, my brethren, if the world hate you.</q>
<rj><qau>1 john iii. 13.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Marvel</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Marvel
<hw>Mar"vel</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To marvel at.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Wyclif.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To cause to marvel, or be surprised; -- used
impersonally.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>But much now me <qex>marveleth</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Rich. the
Redeless.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>marvellous</ent>⟦br⟧
